# Directory reservation for SUNCO Workflow Router durable decision tier.
#
# Phase 52a creates this directory with a .keep placeholder so that the
# namespace exists before Phase 52b runtime writes begin. Content policy:
#
#   - durable tier route decision logs: <YYYYMMDD>-<HHMMSS>-<stage>.json
#     written only when deterministic promotion criteria are met (see
#     .planning/router/DESIGN-v1.md §4.2)
#   - durable pause events: <YYYYMMDD>-<HHMMSS>-PAUSE.json (append-only)
#
# Ephemeral tier lives at .sun/router/session/ (gitignored); this is the
# git-tracked durable counterpart. Entries older than 180 days may be moved
# to .planning/router/archive/ by a future maintenance pass.
#
# Do not delete this .keep file without also archiving all durable decision
# logs present in the directory.
